"Tails include Seahorse, a graphical program to manage OpenPGP keys. You can "
"start it from the top panel clicking *System* → *Preferences* → *Password and "
"Encryption keys*."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Use encrypted storage devices"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
